commit.message:
Merge pull request #33 from jpcima/master

fix the memory leaks
Fix percussive env when being triggered faster that the duration of the envelope
Functionning basic transport plugin (reacts to change in transport stats, good to sync LFOs for example).

New waf system
Basics for transport plugin
Fixes hz to vc returning inf if coming freq is 0
Force gnu++98 standard when compiling FFT to ensure it keeps compiling on later versions of gcc

Merge pull request #24 from drobilla/master

Fix LV2 installation.

Fix LV2 installation.

The recent update of autowaf modularized LV2 support into a proper waf
module.  Loading the "lv2" module is necessary for env.LV2DIR (and the
corresponding configure options) to be defined.
Rewrite of VCF - closer to original AMS source
Dynamic Waves 2 and VC Organ 2 - same as parent plugins but with semitone instead of harmonic/subharmonic
